<br>
Used it all last night in place of epic. Melee's for 83, it seemed to land its stun on every single thing we fought. I never saw it rampage, but then it never got very low on health. Thing regenerates like MAD, and didn't seem to tank significantly worse than the epic pet. I kept cadeau of flame on it all night long.<br>
<br>
A lvl 60 pet....now if it only summoned hehehe. I like that it is comparable to an epic though. I think the epic's damage output is def higher than Ward of Xegony, but I can chain cast Ward, so it's kinda like having a chain castable, slightly weaker epic. Very cool. I think my plan on raids will be start with epic, and if it dies, start chain casting ward of xegony. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27498">www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27498</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
