<br>
Granted, air was focus'd but it generally ended up with numbers like... Epic 4800 air 5400.  No proc on air pet, didn't count procs on epic, but it'd be pretty close i guess.<br>
<br>
I've been favoring air recently, imo it tanks *slightly* better than epic (both focus'd with gloves of dark summoning) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ssslippy>SSSlippy</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 353<br> <font color=#333333>(10/26/02 5:15:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7583.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Who has air focus?</span><hr size=1> Who the heck has the air pet focus.  Who wasted a crown? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tainsumnr>Tain Sumnr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 254<br> <font color=#333333>(10/26/02 5:21:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7583.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 61 Air pet con's at lvl 60</span><hr size=1> People did do those quests before the epic came out you know......... besides, the staff does not focus the 61+ pets  I believe. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tarqal>Tarqal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 137<br> <font color=#333333>(10/26/02 5:22:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7583.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Who has air focus?</span><hr size=1> focused = gloves of dark summoning<br>
